            <title>[LU-3693] Posix copytool fixes - would cause EBADF</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3693</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems that writing to a file which has been open with O_LOV_DELAY_CREATE but hasn&apos;t been assigned a LOVEA yet now fails with EBADF.&lt;/p&gt;

